project.name: atWork Domain v1
project.description: This is the improved version of the classical Logistic Domain

operator.name: move
operator.description: robot move from one station to another

actor.name: Robot
actor.description: The agent truck moves from an origin place to a desination place.

useCase.name: Move to station
useCase.description: The agent robot moves from one station to another station

definition.precondition: - The robot must be at the start location - The end location must be connected to the end location
definition.postcondition: - the truck is at the destination place.

useCase.name: Pick an object
useCase.description: The agent robot picks an object from a station

definition.precondition: -The robot and the object must be in the same station
definition.postcondition: - the package is in the truck; - the truck load is increased.
definition.invariants: - the truck remains at the same place.

useCase.name: Drop an object
useCase.description: The agent truck unloads a package at a place, which can be either a location or an airport.

definition.precondition: - the object must be in the robot
definition.postcondition: - the package is at the place; - the truck load is decreased.
definition.invariants: - the truck remains at the same place.

action.precondition: self.atStation = from and from.connected->exists(s:Station | s = to)
